OL,3,CWoman arrested by Gardai investigating
OL,4,CKyran Durnin murder
OL,6,FA woman has been arrested by Gardai
OL,7,Finvestigating the disappearance and
OL,8,Fmurder of Kyran Durnin.
OL,10,FThe six-year-old boy was reported
OL,11,Fmissing in August 2024, but Gardai
OL,12,Fbelieve he may have died two years
OL,13,Fearlier.
OL,15,FA murder investigation was launched in
OL,16,FOctober 2024.
