OL,3,CWoman arrested by Gardai investigating
OL,4,CKyran Durnin murder
OL,6,FAn Garda Siochana said a woman in her
OL,7,F50s was being held under section 4 of
OL,8,Fthe Criminal Justice Act 1984, at a
OL,9,Fgarda station in the eastern region on
OL,10,FMonday.
OL,12,FA search is also being carried out at
OL,13,Fa home in Drogheda, Co Louth.
OL,15,FGardai say investigations are ongoing.
